docs.text: airplane ! is the story of ted striker ( robert hays ) - an ex-fighter-pilot who has never gotten over the fact that a decision he had to make in the midst of war led to the death of six , er , seven comrades .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: unable to stop living in the past , ted's world fell apart .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: he spent his time moving from city to city without ever having a stable job , and eventually , as we begin this film , is getting dumped by his lover , flight attendant elaine dickinson ( julie hagerty ) .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: in a desperate attempt not to lose her , ted buys a ticket for the same flight elaine is working .

docs.text: unfortunately , she is unsympathetic and even criticizes ted for following her , which leaves him wallowing in self-pity .
